          </div>
          <div class="callout tip">
            <div class="callout-title">
              &#127919; The 5-Step Interview Protocol
            </div>
            <p>
              (1) <strong>Restate</strong> the problem in your own words. (2)
              <strong>Brute force:</strong> state it and its complexity. (3)
              <strong>Optimize:</strong> explain the insight that unlocks the
              better approach. (4) <strong>Code</strong> the optimal solution.
              (5) <strong>Verify:</strong> trace one example by hand, then state
              time/space complexity. This protocol distinguishes a hire from a
              strong hire.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
        <hr class="divider" />
