          <h2 class="sec-title">Today's <em>Plan</em></h2>
          <div class="sched">
            <div class="sched-row">
              <div class="sched-time">5 min</div>
              <div class="sched-desc">
                <strong>Spaced Repetition</strong><br />Write
                <code>two_sum</code> (hash map) and
                <code>group_anagrams</code> from memory. No looking. This ritual
                runs every morning from Day 2 onwards.
              </div>
            </div>
