              <div class="sched-time">1.5 hr</div>
              <div class="sched-desc">
                <strong>Sections 1.1 &rarr; 1.4</strong><br />Two Pointers. Type
                every code block in a Python REPL. Trace 3Sum through
                <code>[-4,-1,-1,0,1,2]</code> by hand before running it.
              </div>
